high_descs: Walk to the edge of the kitchen table behind you.
Grab an apple from the table.
Walk to the microwave on your left.
Put the apple in the microwave, then take it out.
Walk to the kitchen table behind you.
Put the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Heat an apple and replace it.

high_descs: Turn around and face left at the wall to reach the side of the white table.
Pick up the apple in between two knives next to a mug on the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink ahead.
Put the apple inside the microwave, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the front of the white table ahead.
Put the heated apple on the table to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple on a table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to wall, turn left facing the table
Pick up apple off of table
Turn left, walk forward to sink
Put apple in microwave and turn on,  open microwave, remove apple
Turn around, walk back to table
anns.task_desc: Take apple off of table, microwave, and return it to table
